# VANTAZII :D / Backend

# General journey

Customer need to access the app to purchase **points so he can start gamble on games**

if he is correct he will receive a points can be purchased as money .

Customer must only have only one account connected with his phone number .

## Stack-holders :

- Customer can : [Login - Purchase Point  - Receive points to be purchased - gamble on multiple matches ] / update his profile / view history
- Admin to see all customer / manage leagues and matches

##  Payments & Purchase :

- Customers wallet / point system
- From  the platform to the customer
- Payment history & transactions

